		<label>Jumen axe【Second-rate】</label>
		<description>【Second-rate】Melee weapon\n\nAn axe of ancient god soldiers, forged from a large amount of metal, it is carved all over the grain. When holding the axe to stimulate the aura, the axe will emit waves of low chirping, affecting the area of people.</description>
		<graphicData>
			<!--RI_Weapon_JumenAxe-->
			<texPath>Things/Item/Equipment/WeaponMelee/RI_Weapon_JumenAxe</texPath>
			<drawSize>1.4</drawSize>
		</graphicData>
		<statBases>
			<MarketValue>3200</MarketValue>
			<Mass>15</Mass>
		</statBases>
		<weaponTags>
			<li>RI_BetterWeapon_Tag</li>
		</weaponTags>
		<equippedAngleOffset>-90</equippedAngleOffset>
